Semi-final

Brazil received a bye to the final.

21/8 Uruguay  2-1  Guatemala
  [Estadio Brígido Iriarte]
  [Goals: Miguel Angel Peirano 48' 75' / José Luis Bobadilla 78']
  [Ref: Angelo Brassif (USA)]
  [Uruguay: José Luis Sosa, Gualberto De los Santos (Abraham Yeladián 46'), Alvaro Pérez,
            José Alberto Batista (Edgardo Martirena 60'), Santiago Javier Ostolaza,
            Juan Pedro Rabino, Vicente Rudy Rodríguez, Ricardo Perdomo, Miguel Angel Peirano,
            Víctor Haroldo Púa, Luis Heimen.]
  [Guatemala: Ricardo Jeréz Hidalgo; Julio Gómez Rendón, Guillermo Rodríguez,
              Benjamín Monterroso, Édgar Salguero; Jorge Fernández, Walter Claverí,
              Víctor Hugo Méndez; Mynor Méndez, José Luis Bobadilla, Byron Pérez.]

Final

23/8 Uruguay  1-0  Brazil
  [Estadio Brígido Iriarte]
  [Goal: Miguel Angel Peirano 83']
  [Ref: Mario Lira (Chile)]
  [Uruguay: José Luis Sosa, Alvaro Pérez, Santiago Javier Ostolaza, José Alberto Batista,
            Abraham Yeladián, Juan Pedro Rabino, Vicente Rudy Rodríguez, Ricardo Perdomo,
            Miguel Angel Peirano, Víctor Haroldo Púa, Luis Heimen (Edgardo Martirena 76').]
  [Brazil: Hugo; Heitor, Everaldo, Guto, Jorginho; Édson Souza, Dunga, Neto (Adalberto);
           Helinho (Waldir), Marcus Vinícius, Paulinho.]



